								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia Metaverse, a promising candidate for the best crypto presale of 2023, wants to add AI to its metaverse in a big way. Lucidia has come up with a new way to train AI algorithms that involves users in the process, keeps costs low, and makes sure the AI stays responsive and up-to-date. This is a solution to the common problem of training AI algorithms.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Train2Earn Mechanism of Lucidia:</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Train2Earn is a feature of Lucidia Metaverse that lets users train and improve the platform&#8217;s AI algorithms while getting paid for their work. This method has a number of advantages:</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cost savings: By having users train AI, Lucidia doesn&#8217;t have to hire as many AI engineers, which lowers the cost of development.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">User-centered AI: Since the users train the AI themselves, the algorithms will be better at meeting the users&#8217; needs and preferences.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Up-to-date Algorithms: As users keep training the AI, the algorithms will stay up-to-date and get better over time, especially if the number of users keeps growing.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Encouragement for Users to Join: The Train2Earn mechanism gives users another reason to join the Lucidia metaverse, which helps the platform grow.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Availability of Platform:</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia wants to make its platform available on many devices, like Android, iOS, and PC (Windows). The first release will be a PC version that doesn&#8217;t use blockchain, but the first mobile version will work with blockchain from the start.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Choose a Blockchain:</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia has not yet decided on a blockchain that will work well. But the main goal is to choose a gaming-focused environment with low fees and fast transactions to give users the best possible experience.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In conclusion, Lucidia Metaverses&#8217;s new way of training AI and its focus on accessibility and user experience make it a strong candidate for the best crypto presale of 2023.</span></p>					</div>
